    {
      "label": "Transcript",
      "value": "To the President and Members of the Saint Andrews Club Charleston\n\nThe Petition of Jane Adamson, \n\nHumbly Sheweth\n\nThat your Petitioner is a native of Scotland, and is an aged widow in great distress, having lately lost her only son, who was her chief support, any relief that you in your charity may be pleased to grant her will be ever gratefully remembered by\n\nGentlemen\n\nYr. Most Obl. Servt. [your most obliged servant]\n\nJane Adamson\n\nCharleston\n29 Nov 1791"
